  • java.lang.Object
    • universum.studios.android.preference.SharedPreference<E>

    E - Type of the enum implementation of which value should be persisted.

    public final class EnumPreference<E extends Enum>
extends SharedPreference<E>
    A SharedPreference implementation that may be used to persist an Enum value via SharedPreferences.
